Prior to that he was at Monitor
Company, a global consulting

00:00:32.299 --> 00:00:35.480
firm, based out of Cambridge,
Massachusetts, for 13 years,

00:00:35.480 --> 00:00:37.280
as a director, and
as, ultimately,

00:00:37.280 --> 00:00:40.340
